title: Drumkeen
text: Drumkeen () is a village and <a href="townland">townland</a> in <a href="County%20Donegal">County Donegal</a>, Ireland. The village is near the <a href="N13%20road%20%28Ireland%29">N13</a> primary road, about west of <a href="Convoy%2C%20County%20Donegal">Convoy</a>. The village population was 193 at the 2016 census. The local <a href="Association%20football">soccer</a> club, Drumkeen United, play at St Patrick's Park. The village is located just above the <a href="Burn%20Dale">Burn Dale</a>, which flows along the southern edge of the village.
